summary:
➡ I’m an organization ninja who is not afraid to face the most daunting maintenance tasks. I find peace in bringing structure to the table and optimizing resources that saw their better days.

➡ I value high quality work and pay great attention to detail.
Creating a healthy, harmonious workspace is something I strive to do and promote in every professional environment.

➡ I get satisfaction from working efficiently by following reliable procedures while always trying to up my game with smart ideas and clever solutions. 

➡ I’m highly driven by serving others. I seek to make a contribution through sharing my knowledge, experience and practical skills.
